1. Installing EMBASSY MIRA

The EMBASSY MIRA package contains "wrapper" applications providing an 
EMBOSS-style interface to the applications in the original MIRA package 
version 2.8.2 developed by Bastien Chevreux.

Please read the file INSTALL in the EMBASSY MIRA package distribution 
for installation instructions.



